  "name": "RPlog_An_Uneventful_Evening",
  "title": "An Uneventful Evening",
  "summary": "At Plaxton's storied Sandbar cantina on Caspar, the mechanic Orson Tighe and the Jedi Jessalyn Valios settle in for a rare relaxed evening, joined by the Griffon ambassador Wally and the wary Horansi cub Toryn. The brooding, drunken Malus drifts around the bar, unsettling Toryn, who soon slips away. Over brandy and broiled whitefish, Wally enthuses about a brief encounter with Luke Skywalker and his lifelong fascination with the Force, while Orson and Jessalyn trade silent Force-borne messages. Jessalyn's Jedi senses catch Malus whispering to the newcomer Zerae that he killed a man the night before, a confession no ordinary ear could have overheard. She quietly shares the alarming overheard secret with Orson as the supposedly uneventful evening takes on a darker undercurrent, and Malus, looking ill, stumbles off toward the restroom.",
